          "body": "Your C-suite — without the scheduling, without the bottlenecks.",
          "motion": { "type": "fade-up", "delayMs": 300 },
          "visual": { "kind": "image", "asset": "/assets/moments/csuite.png", "alt": "Instant executive guidance" }
        }
      ]
    },
    "why": {
      "id": "why",
      "title": "AI is here, and we have two choices:",
      "body": "We can squeeze more out of people — faster, longer, until they burn out. Or we can use AI to give people back their focus, energy, and creativity. We built PVLSE for the second path. Because when people thrive, so do organizations."
    },
    "wellbeingProductivity": {
      "title": "Wellbeing isn't a perk. It's a performance multiplier.",
      "bullets": [
        "Clear the work no human was meant to do.",
        "Balance workloads in real time.",
        "Nudge rest before burnout hits.",
        "Suggest skill-building that fits real interests."
      ],
      "note": "Balance productivity with human wellbeing for sustainable growth."
    },
    "howItWorks": {
      "id": "how",
      "title": "How PVLSE Works",
